Gnome-Applets
=============

This package contains applets for use with the GNOME panel.  Therefore, it
requires gnome-core to be installed.  To build all applets additional
libraries are needed (libxml, libhttp, libesd, libgtop).


Requirements
------------

You need at least:

    gnome-core-1.4.x; cf. the packages named by gnome-core README.


Optional
--------

    libxml-1.8.6
    libhttp
    libesd
    libgtop
    gnome-vfs
    